text: Vitaly Rudnitsky (born 29 November 1974) is a Belarusian gymnast. He competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Belarus Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Mogilev
